                <note rend="inline" type="source">824.00/179: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stimson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Buenos Aires</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-02-06T11:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 6, 1921—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 4:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>31. Your 15, February 4th. Argentine Government today expressed its intention of
                    recognizing Bolivian Government on the 9th instant. Under Secretary of State
                    stated that Chilean, Brazilian and Japanese Governments have requested
                    information as to the intentions of the Argentine Government in the premises and
                    they have all been informed that the Argentine Government intends to follow the
                    United States in recognizing the Bolivian Government on February 9th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
